Package cs2030.simulator

Class SelfCheckout

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.Server
      • cs2030.simulator.SelfCheckout
  • class SelfCheckout
extends Server
    A class representing a self-checkout counter. A self-checkout counter can perform all functions a Server can perform, the only difference is it shares a unified queue with all other self-checkout counters.
